org.openimaj.video

Class VideoDisplayAdapter<T extends Image<?,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.video.VideoDisplayAdapter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the Image type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    VideoDisplayListener<T>, VideoDisplayStateListener

    public class VideoDisplayAdapter<T extends Image<?,T>>
extends Object
implements VideoDisplayStateListener, VideoDisplayListener<T>
    An adapter for classes that want to listen to certain events that are generated from a video display. This adapter implements both the VideoDisplayListener and the VideoDisplayStateListener.
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
